overview:
Co-founder/CEO of Tuubio Ltd., a startup out of Helsinki, Finland building the future of radio. Jens has been active in the Finnish startup ecosystem since 2009 and begun his own entrepreneurial career in the summer of 2010 with Experq Oy, which was sold onwards in May 2011. Jens holds a BSc.(Econ.) in Finance from the Aalto University School of Economics in Helsinki.

In his free time, Jens is an avid skydiver and takes equal pleasure from music, both as a listener and guitarist.
